txt.en: Find the enemies that left these weapons behind
It appears the Ungoledain have been having their issues with the Gundabad on their journey to Rushgate.
A mix of Ungoladan and Gundabad weapons are strewn about the ground. It would be beneficial to investigate and discover who was the victor.
